      "text": "Good, good. Hey, I wanted to give you a call um I we have an exclusive partnership with Facebook marketplace and I know it's I know it's getting late in the day. You're probably getting ready to go home, so I don't wanna take up too much of your time but um we're working with quite a few different companies in in the area"
