      "recording_attendee_id": "3475d1ed-c199-4b3d-8600-89c269ae367e",
      "order_number": 11,
      "text": "and wanted to see, you know, if it might make sense to set up ten to fifteen minutes to kinda show you what we're all about and how we're driving more leads over to to uh complexes and property management companies."
